首先我们准备半肥瘦的二刀肉1大块
First, we prepare a chunk of half lean half fat “Erdaorou”(The piece of pork near the hind legs)
将猪肉切开之后再去掉猪皮
Cut the pork and remove pork skin
同学们蒸肉糕不能放猪皮否则影响口感
You can't make steamed meatloaf with skin on because it affects the taste
不喜欢猪肉的同学也可以用鱼肉或者鸡肉代替
Substitute pork with chicken or fish if you prefer
去皮之后将肉放入温水中清洗干净
Wash pork with warm water after taking off the skin
这里分享一个小技巧
Pro tip:
猪肉最好温水清洗，冷水会让猪肉凝固
Wash pork with warm water, as cold water makes pork fat solidify
清洗干净之后捞出下一步开始制作
After cleaning let's go to do the next step
首先将猪肉切成厚片
Cut the pork into thick slices
然后将其剁成肉蓉备用
then mince it 
同学们这一步比较消耗耐力
This step is very labour-intensive and requires good stamina
纯手工剁肉大约需要30分钟
It takes about 30 minutes to mince the pork by hand.
嫌麻烦的话也可以交给摊主用绞肉机处理
Feel free to use meat grinder/food processor 
这一步必须将肉剁得越细口感越好
The finer the better.
肉蓉剁好之后下一步开始调制
Next step is seasoning 
首先准备适量的温水
Prepare moderate amount of warm water
加入几根小葱
Add a few green onions
再加入2小块生姜拍散
Add two pieces of smashed ginger
然后用力抓2分钟
And massage vigorously for 2 minutes
这一步的目的是得到姜葱汁
This step is to extract the juice out of green onion and ginger
抓好之后把姜葱捞出丢弃
Remove green onion and ginger
准备鸡蛋5个打入碗中将蛋黄分离
Crack 5 eggs and split the yolks 
然后将蛋黄搅散备用
Beat up the yolks in a bowl and set aside
准备适量的红薯淀粉
Prepare moderate amount of sweet potato starch
碗中加入1:1的清水将其捏散备用
Add 1:1 water into the bowl and mix it
下一步开始调肉泥
Next let's prepare pork paste
盆中加入分好的蛋清
Add the egg whites into the mixing bowl
加入调好的姜葱汁
Add the green onion and ginger juice
再加入一半的红薯 淀粉
Add half of the sweet potato starch
然后将肉抓散拌匀
Stir until fully mixed
同学们切记水淀粉不能一次加入
Don’t add all the starch at once
必须少量多次加入才能完全吸收
Adding it little by little makes it easier to incorporate
水淀粉吸收完成之后再加入2勺食用盐
Add two spoonfuls of salt after slurry (startch + water) is fully absorbed
然后顺着一个方向搅拌上劲备用
Then mix it in one direction
搅拌上劲之后加入适量的青花椒面
Add moderate amount of ground green Sichuan peppercorn 
不能吃麻味的同学可以不加
Skip it you don’t like the numbing sensation from Sichuan peppercorn
再加入少许的胡椒粉
Add a little bit of ground pepper
拌匀之后准备一个方形磨具
Prepare a square baking pan
盆中加入适量的食用油润一遍
Smear a layer of vegetable oil over the inside of the pan
这样的目的是防止肉糕粘连在盆中
This is to prevent sticking
同学们切记边上也要涂抹均匀
Make sure you grease the sides, too
涂抹均匀之后将多余的油倒出
Pour out excess oil
然后将肉泥均匀的放入盆中压紧
Spread the meat paste evenly in the baking pan and press it hard
肉泥压紧之后下一步开始蒸制
Ready for steaming
将制作好的肉泥放入蒸锅中蒸35分钟即可
Steam the meatloaf for 35 minutes
中途肉糕成形之后取出
Take it out when the meatloaf turns solid
将盆中多余的水份倒出
Remove excess liquid
然后加入适量的的蛋黄均匀涂抹在肉糕上面
and smear a layer of egg yolk on top of the meatloaf
嫌麻烦的同学也可以将蛋黄摊成饼盖在上面
Feel free to fry an omelette and cover the meatloaf with it
然后再放入蒸锅蒸制蛋黄熟透
Steam again until eggyolk is cooked
蛋黄熟透之后再次取出涂抹蛋黄蒸制
Repeat
如此反复几次之后肉糕上面即可形成一层黄皮
After repeating for a few times, a golden skin will form
35分钟之后即可将肉糕取出凉透
After 35 minutes of steaming, take out the meatloaf and let it cool down
待肉糕凉透之后再切成厚片即可
Cut it into thick slices after it cools down
一道非常美味营养的蒸肉糕就制作完成
This very tasty dish and nutritious "steamed meatloaf" is completed 
下面开始技术总结
Technical summary:
第一，原材料可以选择鸡鱼肉(猪肉)三种，且方法大致相同
You can use chicken, pork, or fish. Cooking method will be basically the same
第二，蒸肉糕的模具最好大且浅，否则不容易蒸熟透
Use a baking pan that's shallow and wide, so that the meatloaf cooks faster
第三，肉蓉剁得越细口感越嫩
The finer you mince the meat, the more tender it will taste
第四，蒸制的时候火候不能太大，也不能超时蒸制否则肉糕变老
Don't steam over high heat, and don't steam for too long. Overcooked meatloaf can get dry and tough to chew.
蒸肉糕的技术总结完毕
That's it for today's technical summary


